WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.664 --> 00:00:04.945
Oh, pretty butterfly

2
00:00:06.063 --> 00:00:09.156
Where have you gone?

3
00:00:09.234 --> 00:00:11.312
- Are you ready to fly?
- Ready!

4
00:00:11.393 --> 00:00:16.179
We're flying!

5
00:00:19.539 --> 00:00:23.247
One, two, three!

6
00:00:25.883 --> 00:00:27.567
Be careful!

7
00:00:27.648 --> 00:00:29.107
Don't forget to eat!

8
00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:34.250
Dad, when I grow up...

9
00:00:34.450 --> 00:00:36.304
I want to be a nurse, like Mom.

10
00:00:36.352 --> 00:00:38.552
Kartika, you should be a doctor.

11
00:00:39.023 --> 00:00:40.250
Yes.

12
00:00:44.693 --> 00:00:47.122
Ms Ani, Daddy didn't come home last night.

13
00:00:47.203 --> 00:00:48.984
Don't you watch television?

14
00:00:51.719 --> 00:00:56.984
Dodo Rozak committed breaking and entering.

15
00:00:57.039 --> 00:00:59.734
The defendant was also involved
in brutal murder...

16
00:01:00.156 --> 00:01:01.953
Daddy!

17
00:01:06.203 --> 00:01:08.458
I'm Dodo Rozak.

18
00:01:08.539 --> 00:01:14.414
I'm 175 kilocentimeters.

19
00:01:15.078 --> 00:01:16.271
Wait, wait!

20
00:01:16.356 --> 00:01:17.939
He's on death row.

21
00:01:23.484 --> 00:01:27.445
You know what happens
to criminals in this place?

22
00:01:27.811 --> 00:01:29.046
Prison life is tough.

23
00:01:29.117 --> 00:01:30.914
We have to work out a lot.

24
00:01:33.875 --> 00:01:35.583
Now we're brothers.

25
00:01:35.643 --> 00:01:38.357
I have to be nice to people...

26
00:01:38.441 --> 00:01:42.148
So people will be nice to me, too.

27
00:01:42.284 --> 00:01:44.307
- What do you want?
- My daughter.

28
00:01:49.973 --> 00:01:51.197
Daddy!

29
00:01:59.304 --> 00:02:01.929
Is it true that you
murdered Melati Wibisono?

30
00:02:02.010 --> 00:02:04.018
I'm not a bad guy, Sir.

31
00:02:04.940 --> 00:02:08.773
Dodo, you have to make sacrifices.
Including your life.

32
00:02:10.092 --> 00:02:12.280
- Never forget, okay?
- Forget about what?

33
00:02:12.361 --> 00:02:13.736
Never forget about me.

34
00:02:13.799 --> 00:02:15.088
One.

35
00:02:17.776 --> 00:02:18.869
Two.

36
00:02:21.354 --> 00:02:22.611
Three!

37
00:02:26.026 --> 00:02:28.817
I want to go with you!

